flowchart LR
    RT[Route] --> MW[Middleware: auth, ResolveCompany, membership]
    MW --> C[Controller - thin]
    C --> FR[FormRequest - validation]
    C --> S[Service / Action - domain logic + transaction]
    S --> R[Repository - persistence]
    R --> M[Eloquent Model: BelongsToTenant, HasUlid]
    S --> E[Domain Event] --> L[Listener/Job - queued side-effects]
    C --> RES[API Resource - response shape]
